---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout 
    title="Men's Career Coaching: Breaking Through Professional Barriers | Tom Jameson"
    description="Learn how men's career coaching can help you overcome workplace challenges, advance your career, and achieve professional fulfillment. Expert guidance for career growth."
    canonical="https://tomcoaching.com/blog/mens-career-coaching"
>
    <div class="blog-post-container">
        <div class="container">
            <nav class="breadcrumb">
                <a href="/">Home</a> / <a href="/blog">Blog</a> / Men's Career Coaching
            </nav>

            <article class="blog-post">
                <header class="post-header">
                    <div class="post-meta">
                        <span class="category">Career Development</span>
                        <span class="date">December 19, 2024</span>
                    </div>
                    <h1>Men's Career Coaching: Breaking Through Professional Barriers</h1>
                    <p class="post-excerpt">Learn how men's career coaching can help you overcome workplace challenges, advance your career, and achieve professional fulfillment.</p>
                </header>

                <div class="post-content">
                    <p>Men's career coaching addresses the unique challenges that men face in today's professional landscape. From navigating workplace politics to developing leadership skills, career coaching provides targeted support for men seeking to advance their professional lives and achieve greater job satisfaction.</p>

                    <p>Many men struggle with career transitions, whether moving into management roles, changing industries, or starting their own businesses. Professional career coaching helps identify strengths, address limiting beliefs, and develop practical strategies for overcoming obstacles that may be holding you back from reaching your full potential.</p>

                    <p>Effective career coaching for men focuses on building confidence, improving communication skills, and developing emotional intelligence in professional settings. Coaches work with clients to create clear career goals, develop networking strategies, and build the skills necessary for long-term professional success.</p>

                    <p>Whether you're feeling stuck in your current role, considering a career change, or looking to develop leadership capabilities, men's career coaching can provide the guidance and accountability you need to create meaningful professional growth and achieve your career aspirations.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="related-articles">
                    <h3>Related Articles</h3>
                    <div class="related-grid">
                        <a href="/blog/mens-leadership-coaching" class="related-card">
                            <h4>Men's Leadership Coaching: Developing Executive Presence</h4>
                            <p>Build executive presence and leadership skills.</p>
                        </a>
                        <a href="/blog/mens-midlife-coaching" class="related-card">
                            <h4>Men's Midlife Coaching: Navigating Life Transitions</h4>
                            <p>Navigate midlife transitions with confidence.</p>
                        </a>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="post-cta">
                    <h3>Ready to Advance Your Career?</h3>
                    <p>Take the first step towards achieving your professional goals with expert career coaching.</p>
                    <a href="/#contact" class="btn">Book Your Consultation Today</a>
                </div>
            </article>
        </div>
    </div>

    <style>
        .blog-post-container {
            min-height: 100vh;
            background: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 80px 0;
        }

        .breadcrumb {
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            color: #666;
        }

        .breadcrumb a {
            color: #d0c39b;
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        .breadcrumb a:hover {
            color: #172a22;
        }

        .blog-post {
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background: white;
            padding: 3rem;
            border-radius: 12px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }

        .post-header {
            margin-bottom: 3rem;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .post-meta {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 2rem;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
        }

        .category {
            background: #d0c39b;
            color: #172a22;
            padding: 0.3rem 0.8rem;
            border-radius: 20px;
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        .date {
            color: #666;
        }

        .post-header h1 {
            font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            color: #172a22;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
            line-height: 1.2;
        }

        .post-excerpt {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            color: #666;
            font-style: italic;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .post-content {
            line-height: 1.8;
            color: #333;
            margin-bottom: 3rem;
        }

        .post-content p {
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
        }

        .related-articles {
            margin-bottom: 3rem;
            padding-top: 2rem;
            border-top: 1px solid #e9ecef;
        }

        .related-articles h3 {
            font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
            color: #172a22;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        }

        .related-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
            gap: 1.5rem;
        }

        .related-card {
            background: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 1.5rem;
            border-radius: 8px;
            text-decoration: none;
            transition: transform 0.3s ease;
            border: 1px solid #e9ecef;
        }

        .related-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-3px);
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }

        .related-card h4 {
            color: #172a22;
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
        }

        .related-card p {
            color: #666;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            margin: 0;
        }

        .post-cta {
            text-align: center;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #172a22 0%, #1e3a2e 100%);
            color: #d0c39b;
            padding: 2.5rem;
            border-radius: 12px;
        }

        .post-cta h3 {
            font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
            font-size: 1.8rem;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }

        .post-cta p {
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
            opacity: 0.9;
        }

        .btn {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: #d0c39b;
            color: #172a22;
            padding: 15px 30px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(208, 195, 155, 0.3);
        }

        .btn:hover {
            background-color: #c4b082;
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(208, 195, 155, 0.4);
        }

        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .blog-post {
                padding: 2rem;
                margin: 0 1rem;
            }
            
            .post-header h1 {
                font-size: 2rem;
            }
            
            .post-meta {
                flex-direction: column;
                gap: 0.5rem;
            }
        }
    </style>

